description: Discover this beautifully updated floor-through 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom unit that is ideally situated on the East Side. In addition to garage parking and private outdoor space, this home features a spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances, complemented by a breakfast bar and an additional dining area. The generous, light-filled living room has a built in media console and a cozy gas fireplace. The king-size primary suite offers tons of natural light, a substantial walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom. Down the hall, the queen-size bedroom has dual closets and utilizes the oversized hall bath featuring a Jacuzzi tub. With a large private deck, in-unit laundry, central air, dedicated storage, and hardwood floors, this unit really does have it all! This 3 unit pet-friendly association provides extra off-street guest parking and ~1,500 square feet of additional common storage space.Perfectly positioned moments from the beach, shops, dining, and convenient bus lines.
